# 🔥 1. CREATE (Insert)

### ➤ Insert one document

```js
db.users.insertOne({
  name: "Anand",
  age: 25,
  city: "Chennai"
})
```

### ➤ Insert multiple documents

```js
db.users.insertMany([
  { name: "Raj", age: 30 },
  { name: "Priya", age: 22 }
])
```

---

# 🔍 2. READ (Find Queries)

### ➤ Get all documents

```js
db.users.find()
```

### ➤ Pretty format

```js
db.users.find().pretty()
```

### ➤ Condition

```js
db.users.find({ age: 25 })
```

### ➤ Multiple conditions

```js
db.users.find({ age: 25, city: "Chennai" })
```

---

# ⚡ Operators (Very Important)

### ➤ Greater than / Less than

```js
db.users.find({ age: { $gt: 20 } })   // >
db.users.find({ age: { $lt: 30 } })   // <
```

### ➤ Greater than equal / Less than equal

```js
db.users.find({ age: { $gte: 25 } })
db.users.find({ age: { $lte: 30 } })
```

### ➤ Not equal

```js
db.users.find({ age: { $ne: 25 } })
```

### ➤ AND

```js
db.users.find({
  $and: [
    { age: 25 },
    { city: "Chennai" }
  ]
})
```

### ➤ OR

```js
db.users.find({
  $or: [
    { age: 25 },
    { city: "Mumbai" }
  ]
})
```

---

# 🎯 Projection (Select specific fields)

```js
db.users.find({}, { name: 1, age: 1 })
```

👉 `_id` remove panna:

```js
db.users.find({}, { name: 1, _id: 0 })
```

---

# 🔄 3. UPDATE

### ➤ Update one

```js
db.users.updateOne(
  { name: "Anand" },
  { $set: { age: 26 } }
)
```

### ➤ Update many

```js
db.users.updateMany(
  { city: "Chennai" },
  { $set: { country: "India" } }
)
```

### ➤ Increment value

```js
db.users.updateOne(
  { name: "Anand" },
  { $inc: { age: 1 } }
)
```

---

# ❌ 4. DELETE

### ➤ Delete one

```js
db.users.deleteOne({ name: "Anand" })
```

### ➤ Delete many

```js
db.users.deleteMany({ age: { $lt: 20 } })
```

---

# 📊 5. SORT, LIMIT, SKIP

### ➤ Sort

```js
db.users.find().sort({ age: 1 })   // ascending
db.users.find().sort({ age: -1 })  // descending
```

### ➤ Limit

```js
db.users.find().limit(5)
```

### ➤ Skip (pagination)

```js
db.users.find().skip(5).limit(5)
```

---

# 🔥 6. COUNT

```js
db.users.countDocuments({ age: { $gt: 20 } })
```

---

# 🧠 7. DISTINCT

```js
db.users.distinct("city")
```

---

# ⚙️ 8. AGGREGATION (Advanced 🔥)

### ➤ Group by

```js
db.users.aggregate([
  {
    $group: {
      _id: "$city",
      total: { $sum: 1 }
    }
  }
])
```

### ➤ Match + Group

```js
db.users.aggregate([
  { $match: { age: { $gt: 20 } } },
  {
    $group: {
      _id: "$city",
      avgAge: { $avg: "$age" }
    }
  }
])
```

---

# 🔎 9. TEXT SEARCH

```js
db.users.find({
  name: { $regex: "An", $options: "i" }
})
```

---

# 🧩 10. ARRAY QUERIES

```js
db.users.find({ skills: "Java" })
```

```js
db.users.find({
  skills: { $in: ["Java", "Python"] }
})
```

