# 🔥 AGGREGATION (REAL POWER)

## 🧠 16. `$project`

```js
db.users.aggregate([
  {
    $project: {
      name: 1,
      age: 1,
      isAdult: { $gte: ["$age", 18] }
    }
  }
])
```

---

## 🧠 17. `$sort + $limit`

```js
db.users.aggregate([
  { $sort: { age: -1 } },
  { $limit: 3 }
])
```

👉 Top 3 oldest users

---

## 🧠 18. `$lookup` (JOIN 🔥)

```js
db.orders.aggregate([
  {
    $lookup: {
      from: "users",
      localField: "userId",
      foreignField: "_id",
      as: "userDetails"
    }
  }
])
```

👉 SQL JOIN equivalent 💯

---

## 🧠 19. `$unwind`

```js
db.users.aggregate([
  { $unwind: "$skills" }
])
```

👉 Array split pannum

---

## 🧠 20. `$group with sum`

```js
db.orders.aggregate([
  {
    $group: {
      _id: "$product",
      totalSales: { $sum: "$amount" }
    }
  }
])
```

