# 🎯 BONUS (PRO LEVEL 🔥)

## 🧠 21. Pagination (real-world)

```js
db.users.find()
  .skip( (page - 1) * limit )
  .limit(limit)
```

---

## 🧠 22. Case insensitive exact match

```js
db.users.find({
  name: { $regex: "^anand$", $options: "i" }
})
```

